Install minikube

https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/



to apply deployment in k8s

kubectl apply -f $name_of_deployment.yaml

to apply services in k8s

kubectl apply -f $name_of_services.yaml

to apply secrets in k8s

kubectl apply -f $name_of_secrets.yaml


to show Deployment, Services and Secrets

kubectl get deployment 

kubectl get services

kubectl get secrets

